%h3
  JSON Summary
%p
  Along with 'rvm
  %selectors
    rake X' you can add the --json flag prior to the word 'rake' and a JSON summary will be printed out at the end of the run.
%h3
  YAML Summary
%p
  Along with 'rvm
  %selectors
    rake X' you can add the --yaml flag prior to the word 'rake' and a YAML summary will be printed out at the end of the run.
